---
description: Prevents agents from hand-editing generated plugin files
globs: [".cursor-plugin/**", ".claude-plugin/**", ".opencode/**", ".openhands/**", "AGENTS.md", "opencode.json", ".mcp.json", "hooks/setup-cli"]
alwaysApply: false
---

Files matching these globs are generated by `mcp-plugin-gen` from `mcp-plugin.toml`.
Do not edit them directly. Edit the canonical sources and commit — the pre-commit
hook regenerates all platform copies automatically.

Canonical sources:
- `mcp-plugin.toml` — server config, skill/rule/hook declarations
- `skills/*/SKILL.md` — skill content (path declared in mcp-plugin.toml)
- `rules/*.mdc` — rule content (path declared in mcp-plugin.toml)
